\begin_layout Standard
Pick 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\sin\theta=\cos\theta$
\end_inset

, or 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta=\frac{\pi}{4}$
\end_inset

.
 Now:
